response.original_title: Who Am I? Who I Am!
response.overview: The very first sport/biography documentary feature length film in Vietnam about Goalkeeper Tan Truong, the player has the most scandals and doubts about "dirty matches" in Vietnam football history. A match-fixing cheater or just a bad luck guy? A disappointed dude and a loser in the team? He made stupid mistakes unbelievably. But he also had incredible saves unexpectedly. His career and his life has got full of challenges, ups and downs.
response.title: Who Am I? Who I Am!
